description:
Test Case 3: Hybrid Testing.
1. Authenticated context is injected via fixture (API Login -> LocalStorage).
2. We add a product to the cart via the API.
3. We open the UI and navigate straight to checkout, saving execution time.

steps.name: 1. Setup test data via API (Add to cart)
2. Navigate to product and add to cart (Fast UI)
4. Step 1: User is already logged in (Validated by UI)
